{"title":"街头书亭","authors":["王耀宗"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":4,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"街头书亭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王耀宗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你虽小，却如同一块磁铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以所有的磁能，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感应无数急切的渴念；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是意外发现的恒星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辐射出无限的光和热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众多青春的行星围绕你旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那曾贫乏的心灵得到充盈。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}